Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:14.64,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,總是不能如意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:19.44,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,每天戰戰兢兢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:28.07,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,把自己的價值觀強加於人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:31.12,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,-15)}又倍感痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:40.42,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,儘管如此 我們也要生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.63,0:22:46.67,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,就算受傷 就算流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:51.93,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,明天也仍將到來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:57.52,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,不要哭泣 無論到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:02.94,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,我們也會面對
